The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Metro | Good Morning
                                                                                                               Good Morning
      Hello It's Sunday , March 29 , 2009                
	Storytelling     Attend a storytelling session on Mahabharata at Starmark, 3 Lord Sinha Road, 5pm.         
	Cultural    Be there at a special cultural programme on the occasion of The Mothers first arrival day in Pondicherry at The Aurobindo Institute of Culture, 3 Regent Park, 6pm.        
	Eye on art    Take a look at Yours Sincerely, a work by Hema Upadhyay at Bose Pacia, 11am to 7pm.  Move on to Recent Works, an exhibition by Chandana Hore at Seagull Arts and Media Resource Centre, 2pm-8pm.  Browse through The Rhythm of Colour, an exhibition at Idiyas Art Gallery, 15 Dover Road, 10.30am to 7pm.                                                                                                                                                                
